snippet.title: Johnny vs AH (Fairfax) Judge Azcarate's 1st Order Seems to be Fair
snippet.description:
In this video we will talk about the 1st order for the Johnny Depp vs Amber Heard case for April 2022 in Fairfax VA.  Judge Azcarate has taken over for the retiring Judge White and has issued her 1st order in this case.  Thankfully,  it seems that she is going to be a fair judge and that is truly all that is needed for this case.  A special thank you to The Real Laura B on Twitter for all of her hard work and a special thanks to my dear friend Mary Sue for keeping me up on everything ❤ 

You can help me with the expenses of running this channel and help with the expenses of attending the VA trial by donating to my PayPal at https://paypal.me/TammyTalksAbout?locale.x=en_US
